CONSTANTS Msg, MaxQueueLength

                  
Remove(i, seq) ==   [j \in 1..(Len(seq)-1) |-> 
                        IF j < i THEN
                            seq[j]
                        ELSE
                            seq[j+1]]

RandomIndex (seq) == CHOOSE x \in 1..Len(seq) : x < Len(seq)
                                         
